org.digijava.module.aim.dbentity

Interface FundingInformationItem

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmpFundingDetail, AmpFundingMTEFProjection, FundingPledgesDetails

    public interface FundingInformationItem
    an item which holds information regarding a funding detail (e.g. currently AmpFundingDetail or AmpFundingMTEFProjection) it fixes the fact that MTEFProjection are not kept as funding items in AMP - hence this interface tries to unify them
